title: Data Analysis
text:
import pandas as pd

df = pd.read_csv('lightcast_job_postings.csv', low_memory=False)

columns_to_drop = [
    "ID", "URL", "ACTIVE_URLS", "DUPLICATES", "LAST_UPDATED_TIMESTAMP",
    "NAICS2", "NAICS3", "NAICS4", "NAICS5", "NAICS6",
    "SOC_2", "SOC_3", "SOC_5"
]
df.drop(columns=columns_to_drop, inplace=True)
